---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Mit Freuden";
const description =
  "What brings joy to life? That's right: it's really, really well-made software. We think so too.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} locale="en">
  <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-12 text-zinc-800">
    <div class="mb-20 lg:mb-24">
      <div class="flex gap-3 items-center mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl tracking-tight font-light text-zinc-900">
          Mit Freuden
        </h1>
        <svg
          class="h-16 lg:h-24"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 40 40"
        >
          <!-- Square Brackets [ ] - happy eyes ^^ -->
          <g>
            <path
              d="M 10 4 L 4 4 L 4 36 L 10 36"
              fill="none"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 30 4 L 36 4 L 36 36 L 30 36"
              fill="none"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 10 24 Q 20 32 30 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 12 18 Q 14 15 16 18"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              fill="none"></path>
            <path
              d="M 24 18 Q 26 15 28 18"
              stroke="black"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              fill="none"></path>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xl/8 lg:text-2xl/10 font-serif">
        What brings joy to life? That's right: it's
        really, <span class="italic">really</span> well-made software.
        <span class="italic block mt-2 lg:mt-3"> We think so too.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight leading-9 mb-3 md:mb-5">
        Complete solutions that deliver on their promises
      </h2>

      <p class="font-serif max-w-2xl md:max-w-3xl text-lg/8 text-pretty">
        We develop
        <span class="font-bold">complete, ready-to-use software</span> together with you
        – from the initial idea to smooth production operation. Our solutions are
        web-based and run on all platforms. Including native mobile apps for iOS and
        Android if needed. This way you reach your users everywhere, without
        compromising on performance or user experience.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight leading-9 mb-3 md:mb-5">
        Software that brings joy
      </h2>

      <p class="font-serif max-w-2xl md:max-w-3xl text-lg/8 text-pretty">
        What good is the best technology if nobody enjoys working with it? Really,
        really good software must not only function, it should
        also <span class="font-bold">bring joy</span>. That's why we focus on intuitive
        usability and design that not only looks good, but enables simple and functional
        operation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight leading-9 mb-3 md:mb-5">
        Experience that moves industries
      </h2>

      <p class="font-serif max-w-2xl md:max-w-3xl text-lg/8 text-pretty">
        Our team has implemented projects in the most diverse sectors –
        from <span class="font-bold">retail to energy to warehouse logistics</span>.
        Every industry has its own challenges, and we know how to master them.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight leading-9 mb-3 md:mb-5">
        Future-proof through proven technology
      </h2>

      <p class="font-serif max-w-2xl md:max-w-3xl text-lg/8 text-pretty">
        We rely on <span class="font-bold">proven, future-proof</span> technologies that
        grow with your business. Our focus is on B2B solutions such as workflow
        automation, data visualization, or complex logistics systems that have been
        successfully deployed for years. We deliver software not only quickly and
        securely, but also scalably – from startups to enterprise solutions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight leading-9 mb-3 md:mb-5">
        We are reliable partners
      </h2>

      <p class="font-serif max-w-2xl md:max-w-3xl text-lg/8 text-pretty">
        For us, software development is more than just writing code.
        We <span class="font-bold">live your projects</span> with you, understand your
        goals, and develop solutions that truly fit you. No standard packages, no half
        measures. Custom-built software that advances your business and brings you and
        your team joy day after day.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-30 mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight font-normal leading-9 mb-5 md:mb-5">
        Sounds good?
      </h2>

      <p class="font-serif max-w-2xl md:max-w-3xl text-2xl/10 text-pretty mb-2">
        Then let's talk. We look forward to <span class="italic">your</span> project.
      </p>
      <p class="font-serif max-w-2xl md:max-w-3xl text-2xl/10 text-pretty">
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@mitfreuden.com"
          class="underline underline-offset-3 transition-all hover:text-amber-800/60"
          >Say hello</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
